wild pig
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a descendant of domestic pigs released by Europeans since Cook's first voyage.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:also bush pig, cooker
